quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  4,38,"Na ba bandi batanga imitungo yabo (bagamije) kwiyereka abantu, batanemera Allah n’umunsi w’imperuka. Kandi uwo Shitani azabera inshuti, azaba agize inshuti mbi"
  4,39,"Byari kubatwara iki iyo baza kwemera Allah n’umunsi w’imperuka, bakanatanga mu byo Allah yabagabiye? Kandi Allah arabazi bihagije"
  4,40,"Mu by’ukuri, Allah ntahuguza (igikorwa cy’ibiremwa bye) kabone n’iyo cyaba kingana n’akantu gato cyane kadashobora kubonwa n’ijisho; ariko iyo ari keza (gakozwe), aragatubura akanagahembera ingororano zihambaye ziturutse iwe"
  4,41,"Ubwo bizaba bimeze bite (ku munsi w’imperuka), igihe tuzazana umuhamya (intumwa) uturutse muri buri muryango, nawe (Muhamadi) tukakuzana uri umuhamya kuri abo (watumweho)"
  4,42,"Kuri uwo munsi, ba bandi bahakanye bakanigomeka ku ntumwa (Muhamadi) bazifuza ko iyo isi iza kuba yarabamize, bakaba barigumiye mu mva (kugira ngo batagira icyo babazwa), nyamara nta cyo bazahisha Allah"
  4,43,"Yemwe abemeye! Ntimukegere isengesho mwasinze kugeza igihe musobanukiwe ibyo muvuga (mugaruye ubwenge) ndetse n’igihe mufite Janaba (mwagiranye imibonano n’abagore banyu cyangwa mwasohotswemo n’intanga mukaba mutariyuhagira) -keretse abanyura mu musigiti bitambukira cyangwa se abari ku rugendo-; kugeza mwiyuhagiye umubiri wose. Kandi nimuba murwaye cyangwa muri ku rugendo, cyangwa se umwe muri mwe avuye mu bwiherero, cyangwa mwabonanye n’abagore banyu ntimubone amazi, mujye mukora Tayamumu mwisukure mukoresheje igitaka gisukuye, mugihanaguze uburanga bwanyu no ku maboko yanyu (ku biganza byanyu). Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Uhanaguraho ibyaha, Umunyembabazi"
  4,44,"Ese ntiwamenye (yewe Muhamadi) ba bandi bahawe ingabire yo gusobanukirwa igitabo (Tawurati) bagahitamo ubuyobe, bakanashaka ko (namwe) muyoba inzira igororotse"